<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 5 (Milla) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ミラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Milla</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>デューク</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Duke</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ジュード</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Jude</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どうしたんだ、そんな難しい顔をして？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's wrong? Why the long face?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>人間は愚かだ。
彼らが犠牲になってまで守りたかったのは
こんな愚かな種族だというのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Humans are fools. Even if they
become sacrifices for it, they
wish to protect this foolish race?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>35</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>腹が減っているのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are you hungry?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>絶対にちがうよ、ミラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That is definitely not the problem, Milla.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>世界は一度、やり直されねばならない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This world must be remade.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>35</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちょうどセネルにもらったパンがある。
一つどうだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have just enough bread here that Senel gave me.
Do you want one?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>その為に私は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It is for that purpose that I...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>35</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シェリアにもらった焼き鳥丼もつけよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You can even put it with the grilled chicken
rice bowl that Cheria gave to me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ、お前は？
私の邪魔をするつもりか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who are you? Do you intent to get in my way?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>35</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マルタはなにもくれなかったな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Marta didn't gave me anything.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……いいだろう。
人間を守りたければ、お前の覚悟を示せ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Very well. If you wish to protect humanity,
demonstrate your resolve to me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>35</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え、なにこれ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? What's going on?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
